# A material that illustrates a common use for local reflection maps (defined in
# a material).
#
# This material is highly reflective with no diffuse or ambient contribution.
# Its reflection map is an image with silver streaks that yields a chrome
# appearance when viewed as a reflection.
#
# Example taken from the MTL specification.

Ka 0 0 0
Kd 0 0 0
Ks .7 .7 .7
illum 1
refl -type sphere chrome.rla
